<script>

function defaultCase(MetaRefiner)
{
    if ($(".js-location_list li").length==0) {
        var liLocation = $('<li/>', {
            'class':'selected_location',
            'text':'Île-de-France',
            'data':{'label': 'Île-de-France',
 'place': {'code':'2238','param':'div','value':'Île-de-France'}, 
'actionCriterion': "change"}
        }).appendTo('.js-location_list');

        $('<a/>', {
            'class':'refine__localisation_delete',
            'text':'X',
        }).appendTo(liLocation);}


  if($("input[name='idtt']:checked").length==0)
  {$("#block_idtt_idtt_1").click();}

    MetaRefiner.refinerUi.UpdateModel();
}

function refreshList(MetaRefiner, pushState, pageList, pageMap) {
    // est-ce que l'on affiche la refonte 2017 ?
    var refonte2017 = Config.versionB;
    window.scrollTo(0, 0);
    defaultCase(MetaRefiner);
    var query = MetaRefiner.refiner.GetQuery();

    $(".metaRefinerHeader .open").removeClass("open");
    $(".metaRefinerHeader .onfocus").removeClass("onfocus");
    $("#mrLayout").hide();
    $(".mrHabitation").removeClass("hiddenCriteria");
    $(".mrConstruction").addClass("hiddenCriteria");

    // Projet «Construire sa maison»
    if ($("#block_idtt_idtt_18").is(":checked")) {
        $(".mrHabitation").addClass("hiddenCriteria");
        $(".mrConstruction").removeClass("hiddenCriteria");
    }

    // patch de la requête pour gérer les spécificités métier
    query = MetaRefiner.patchQuery(query);

    if (window.history && window.history.pushState) {
        if (pushState) {
            var newUrl = location.protocol + '//' + Config.page.pageUrl + '?' + query;
            history.pushState({refineModel: MetaRefiner.refineModel}, null, newUrl);
        }
    }
    else {
        document.location.href = location.protocol + '//' + Config.page.pageUrl + '?' + query;
        return true;
    }

    // build slider

    function sliderOrArgent() {

        $('.gold .slides').each(function(){
            if ($(this).children('img').length > 1) {
                $(this).slidesjs({
                    width: 250,
                    height: 250,
                    navigation: true
                    // start: 1,
                    // play: {
                    //   auto: true
                    // }
                });
            }
        });

        // used temporary : pole_po needs slider instead of OR which is not on prod yet
        $('.pole_position .slides').each(function () {
            if ($(this).children('img').length > 1) {
                $(this).slidesjs({
                    width: 165,
                    height: 165,
                    navigation: true
                });
            }
        });
    }

    // Init loader
    var loader = '<div class="loader"><img class="chargement" alt="chargement" src="/z/produits/sl/sv6_annonces/new_recherche/img/ajax-loader_transparent.gif" /><span class="chargement">Chargement</span></div>';
    $(".liste_resultat").html(loader);

    var templateSelector = "#template-listing",
        url = (refonte2017 ? "/list,json,listing_list_ab.json" : "/list,json,listing_list.json");

    if(!pageMap) {
        return Promise.resolve($.getJSON(url, query, function (data) {
            var listingListTemplate,
                nbResultsqPage = data.title.nbResultsqPage,
                legalNotices,
                nb_resultat = parseInt(data.title.numListings),
                listingList = $("section.liste_resultat, section.liste_noresultat");

            if (document.location.search.indexOf("idtt=0") !== -1) {
                $("button[data-layer=refine__facette_typetransaction]").parent().hide();
            }

            if (data.cloudMediaParams && data.cloudMediaParams.length !== 0) {
                Config.cloudMediaParams = data.cloudMediaParams;
            }

            if (data.ezakusParams && data.ezakusParams.length !== 0) {
                Config.ezakusParams = data.ezakusParams;
            }

            if (SL) {
                if (SL.CloudMedia) {
                    SL.CloudMedia.init();
                }
            }

            // refresh of Ezakus tag
            if (SLG.Ezakus && SLG.Ezakus.length !== 0) {
                SLG.Ezakus.addTag();
            }

            // Updates the content bloc with the no results page
            // This part clone the selected criterion list and fill the no results template with this criterions
            // Then it renders the template in place of the current list
            if (nb_resultat === 0) {

                // If the current display is result, we have to display the no result section
                if (listingList.hasClass("liste_resultat")) {

                    // Toggle class
                    listingList.removeClass("liste_resultat");
                    listingList.addClass("liste_noresultat");
                }

                var noResultsTemplate = $("#template-no-results").html(),
                    noResultsHTML = Mustache.to_html(noResultsTemplate, {});

                // on recharge le title
                $('.title_nbresult').html('');
                $('h1').html(data.title.htmlContent);

                // Replace the content with no results page
                listingList.html(noResultsHTML);

                // Move Google Adsense after listing no result
                if ($('#preliste_containeur_google_adsense')) {
                    $("#preliste_containeur_google_adsense").detach().appendTo('.liste_noresultat');
                }

            }
            // Results found
            else {
                listingListTemplate = $(templateSelector).html();

                if (listingListTemplate) {
                    SLG.Utils.Renderer.render(listingList, listingListTemplate, data);
                }

                if (listingList.hasClass("liste_noresultat")) {
                    // Toggle class
                    listingList.addClass("liste_resultat");
                    listingList.removeClass("liste_noresultat");
                }

                //phrases de séparation recherche par quartier
                if (nbResultsqPage) {
                    $('.title_search_idq').html(nbResultsqPage);
                }

                //rechargement fil d'ariane
                $('.main .filariane').html(data.fil_ariane);

                // Hide the transaction type for sold properties idf idtt=0

                // on recharge le title
                var title_nbresult = SELOGER.UTILS.formatMillier(data.title.numListings) + ' annonce';

                title_nbresult += parseInt(data.title.numListings) > 1 ? 's' : '';

                $('.title_nbresult').html(title_nbresult);
                $('h1').html(data.title.htmlContent);


                $('.main .create_ali').removeClass('hide');

                //legalNotices
                legalNotices = $('<div/>').html(data.legalNotices).text();
                $('.mentions_footer').html(legalNotices);

                $(".annonce__footer__pagination").replaceWith(data.paginateHtmlContent);

                if (typeof(sliderOrArgent) != "undefined") {
                    sliderOrArgent();
                }


                // version pure jQuery
                $('.liste_resultat').trigger('reloadRefineEnd');

                // version pure JS
                var evt = new CustomEvent('refineReloaded');
                document.querySelector('.liste_resultat').dispatchEvent(evt);
            }
            if (typeof(_setClickArticleListing) != "undefined") {
                _setClickArticleListing();
            }

            if (typeof(avis_immo) != "undefined") {
                avis_immo();
            }
            // Launch trigger on send request listingList
            if (pageList) {
                $(document).trigger('onRequestListingList', {nbListing: nb_resultat, query: query, data: data});
            }

        ///ici
        }));
    }
    else{

        var MultiList = function(selectorList, factory, service) {
            var that = this;

            this.nbCountList = undefined;
            this.titleCount = " ";
            this.firstLoad = true;
            this.hideVedettePixel = 1000;

            this.pixelScroll = 0;
            this.withVedette = false;
            this.list = new SeLoger.List.InfinityList(
                $(selectorList)[0],
                {
                    onLoadStart: function() {},
                    onLoadEnd: function(){
                        that.onListLoad.apply(that, arguments);
                    },
                    onClickElement: function(e) {},
                    onScroll: function(pixel) {
                        that.pixelScroll = pixel;
                        that.onScroll();
                    },
                    onOverElement: function (e) {
                        map.CloseAllAnnonce();
                        map.OpenAnnonce(parseInt(e.data.id));
                    },
                    onOutElement: function (e) {
                        map.CloseAllAnnonce();
                        map.CloseAnnonce(parseInt(e.data.id));
                    },
                    activateRequest: 1000 //pixel avant la fin
                },
                new factory(),
                new service(1)
            );
        };
        MultiList.prototype = {
            onScroll: function () {
                var jQ_vedette = $('.right_column .flagship');
                var jQ_liste = $('.right_column .liste_resultat');

                if((this.pixelScroll > this.hideVedettePixel) && this.withVedette) {
                    jQ_vedette.hide();
                    jQ_liste.addClass('fullheight');
                } else if(this.pixelScroll <= this.hideVedettePixel) {
                    jQ_vedette.show();
                    jQ_liste.removeClass('fullheight');
                }
            },

            loadAllList: function(query) {
                this.nbCountList = this.hyphen = undefined;
                this.firstLoad = true;
                this.separator = false;

                return this.list.reload({ search: query, page: 1}).then(function() {
                    mustach_vedette(query);
                });
            },

            onAddAnnonceFavorisSuccess: function(idAnnonce) {
                for(var i = 0 ; i < this.list.elements.length ; i ++) {
                    if(this.list.elements[i].id.toString() === idAnnonce.toString()) {
                        var el = 
$(".liste_resultat #annonce-" + this.list.elements[i].data.id + "-" + 
this.list.elements[i].data.publicationId + " .add_fav_map");
                        
el.removeClass("action-add").addClass("action-succes").find("button").attr("data-tooltip",
 "Supprimer des favoris");
                    }
                }
            },

            onDeleteAnnonceFavorisSuccess: function(idAnnonce) {
                for(var i = 0 ; i < this.list.elements.length ; i ++) {
                    if(this.list.elements[i].id.toString() === idAnnonce.toString()) {
                        var el = 
$(".liste_resultat #annonce-" + this.list.elements[i].data.id + "-" + 
this.list.elements[i].data.publicationId + " .add_fav_map");
                        
el.removeClass("action-succes").addClass("action-add").find("button").attr("data-tooltip",
 "Ajouter aux favoris");
                    }
                }
            },

            initAnnoncesFavoris: function() {
                var that = this;
                if(window.EspacePerso && window.EspacePerso.DevApi) {
                    window.EspacePerso.DevApi.recupererAnnoncesIds(function(annonces) {
                        annonces.forEach(function(annonceId) {
                            that.onAddAnnonceFavorisSuccess(annonceId);
                        });
                    });
                }
            },

            onListLoad: function(data, elements, total) {

                initCarousel('.right_column 
.liste_resultat .annonce_map.Or, .right_column .liste_resultat 
.annonce_map.PolePo');
                this.nbCountList = parseInt(total);
                this.titleCount = data.data.title;
                if (this.firstLoad === true) {
                    this.onAllListLoadFirstTime(data.data.hyphen);
                }
                this.addClassToPropertyRows(this.hyphen, total);

                this.initAnnoncesFavoris();
            },

            onAllListLoadFirstTime: function(hyphen) {
                var that = this;

                this.firstLoad = false;
                this.hyphen = hyphen;
                $(".type_annonces").text("");

                if (this.nbCountList != 0) {
                    var txt1 = "annonce ";
                    var txt1b = "localisée ";
                    var txt1c = "dans la zone";
                    var txt2 = "annonce ";
                    var txt2b = "non localisée ";

                    var nbtotal = parseInt(this.nbCountList);
                    var localizedCount = hyphen - 1;
                    var unlocalizedCount = nbtotal - localizedCount;
                    var texttitle = nbtotal > 1 ? "annonces " : "annonce ";

                    $(".title_nbresult").text(SELOGER.UTILS.formatMillier(nbtotal));
                    $(".title_wrapper h1").text(texttitle);

                    if(hyphen !== undefined && localizedCount > 0) {
                        $(".type_annonces").html('dont ' + SELOGER.UTILS.formatMillier(localizedCount) + ' sur la carte');
                    }
                }
                else {
                    var $popup = $('#drawingPopup');
                    if(this.nbCountList == 0) {

                        /*var flag = refiner.GetModel().places.length;

                         if (flag) {
                         
$popup.find('span').text("Aucun résultat. Supprimez les critères 
discriminants ou élargissez la zone de recherche");
                         } else {
                         
$popup.find('span').text("Aucun résultat. Votre dernière recherche a été
 effacée, renseignez une localité pour obtenir des résultats");
                         }*/

                        $popup.fadeIn();
                    }
                    else {
                        $popup.fadeOut();
                    }
                    // On n'a pas de résultats dans la liste 2, donc on n'affiche que la première liste, et on
                    // n'affiche pas les onglets
                    var texteA = "annonces";
                    $(".head_list").hide();
                    $(".title_nbresult").text(this.nbCountList);
                    if (this.nbCountList<=1)
                    {texteA="annonce"}
                    $(".title_wrapper h1").text(texteA);
                    $(".type_annonces").html(this.titleCount);
                }
                if($(".refine__limit").css("display")=="none")
                {$('.refine__broaden').hide();}
                else{$('.refine__broaden').show();}


                var event = window.EspacePerso && window.EspacePerso.Events ? window.EspacePerso.Events : null;

                if(event) {
                    event.on('EVENT_CONNECT_SUCCESS', function() {
                        that.initAnnoncesFavoris();
                    });
                    event.on('EVENT_ANNOUNCE_ADD_SUCCESS', function(params) {
                        that.onAddAnnonceFavorisSuccess(params.IdAnnonce);
                        onAddAnnonceFavorisSuccessMap(params.IdAnnonce);
                    });

                    event.on('EVENT_ANNOUNCE_DELETE_SUCCESS', function (params) {
                        that.onDeleteAnnonceFavorisSuccess(params.IdAnnonce);
                        onDeleteAnnonceFavorisSuccessMap(params.IdAnnonce);
                    });
                }
            },

            addClassToPropertyRows: function (hyphen, nbTotal) {
                // adding classes
                var count = 1;
                var rowClass = 'localized';
                var unlocalizedCount = parseInt(nbTotal - (parseInt(hyphen) - 1));
                var that = this;
                $('.liste_resultat > ul > li').each(function(){
                    if (!$(this).hasClass('localized') && !$(this).hasClass('unlocalized')) {
                        if (count >= hyphen) {
                            rowClass = 'unlocalized';
                        }
                        $(this).addClass(rowClass);

                        if (rowClass === 'unlocalized' && that.separator === false) {
                            // ajout du séparateur texte entre les annonces localisées et non localisées
                            $separator = $('<li class="separateur">' + unlocalizedCount + (unlocalizedCount > 1 ? ' annonces ' : ' annonce ') + 'sans adresse renseignée<button class="delete_title_idq"></button></li>');
                            $separator.children('.delete_title_idq').on('click', function() {
                                $(this).parent('.separateur').hide();
                            });
                            $('li.localized + .unlocalized').before($separator);
                            that.separator = true;
                        }
                    }
                    count++;
                });
            }
        };

    }
}



function initRefine(map) {

    var metaRefinerOptions = {
        'updateModelCb': function () {
            if (
                
($("#block_construction_idtypebiena_16").is(":checked") && 
$("#block_construction_idtypebien_4").is(":checked"))
                || 
($("#block_construction_idtypebiena_16").not(":checked") && 
$("#block_construction_idtypebien_4").not(":checked"))
                || ($("#block_construction_idtypebiena_16").is(":checked"))
            ) {
                $(".pieces").parent().removeClass("disabled");
                $(".block_pieces .hiddenCriteria, .block_chambres .hiddenCriteria").removeClass("hiddenCriteria");
                $(".block_pieces .child_title, .block_chambres .child_title").show();
                $(".block_pieces .conditions, .block_chambres .conditions").removeClass("conditions").addClass("bypass");
            }
            else if 
($("#block_construction_idtypebiena_16").not(":checked") && 
$("#block_construction_idtypebien_4").is(":checked")) {
                $(".block_pieces .bypass").removeClass("bypass").addClass("conditions");
                $(".block_pieces input").attr("checked", false);
            }

            cb();
            optionSwitch();
            if( $(".refine__localisation_liste li").length !=0) {
                
updateLimits($(".refine__localisation_liste 
li:last-child").data().place.param + "=" + 
$(".refine__localisation_liste li:last-child").data().place.code);
            }
            
            if (typeof location.search.split("?")[1] != "undefined") {
                if (location.search.split("?")[1].indexOf("naturebien") === -1 && !Config.seo) {
                    var newUrl = location.protocol + '//' + Config.page.pageUrl + location.search + '&naturebien=1,2,4';

                    if (window.history && window.history.pushState ) {
                        history.pushState(null, null, newUrl);
                    } else {
                        document.location.href = newUrl;
                        return true;
                    }
                }
            }


            if 
($("#block_construction_idtypebiena_16").is(":checked") && 
$("#block_construction_idtypebien_4").is(":checked")) {

                $(".block_pieces .hiddenCriteria").removeClass("hiddenCriteria");
            }
            else if 
($("#block_construction_idtypebiena_16").not(":checked") && 
$("#block_construction_idtypebien_4").is(":checked")) {
                $(".pieces").parent('.tdb').addClass("disabled");
                $("#pieces").html('');
            }

            if ($("input#block_type_bien_block_habitation_3").is(":checked")) {
                $(".pieces").parent('.tdb').addClass("disabled");
                $("#pieces").html('');
            }
        },
        'annoncesCounterService': location.protocol + '//www.seloger.com/list,includes,annoncesToDisplay.json'
    };
    var ancien_count=0;// variable compteur pour le bug SS-335
    var pageIndex="default";
    var pageList=false;
    var pageMap=false;
    var pageVenteAcheter=false;
    if($(".main-listing").length!=0)
    {pageIndex="list";
        pageList=true;
    } else if ($("#lifemap-app").length!=0) {
        pageIndex="map";
        pageMap=true;
    }
    else if($(".venteAcheter_btn").length!=0)
    {
        pageVenteAcheter=true;
    }

    if (pageMap) {
        metaRefinerOptions.annoncesCounterService = location.protocol + "//www.seloger.com/map,services,count-announces.json";
        metaRefinerOptions.annoncesCounterServiceKey = "nbgeoloc";
    }
    var formatBudget = function(value) {//sépare les milliers d'un nombre par un espace / compatible tout navigateurs
       return value.toString().replace(/\B(?=(\d{3})+(?!\d))/g, " ");
    };

    var patch5Plus=function () {
        var query = location.search;
        if(query=="" && location.pathname.indexOf("type-5-pieces")!=-1)
        {$(".block_pieces input[value=5]").prop("checked", true)}

        if(query.indexOf("nb_pieces=") != -1 )
        {
            var nbpieces=query.split("nb_pieces=")[1].split("&")[0];
            if (nbpieces.indexOf("5%20et%20")!=-1)
            {$(".block_pieces input[value=5]").prop("checked", true)}
        }
        if(query.indexOf("nb_chambres=") != -1)
        {
            var nb_chambres=query.split("nb_chambres=")[1].split("&")[0];
            if (nb_chambres.indexOf("5%20et%20")!=-1)
            {$(".block_chambres input[value=5]").prop("checked", true)}
        }
    }
    // Callbadk function when update model
    var cb = function () {
        var $typedebienRecap = $('.typedebienRecap'),
            typedebien = '',
            isTerrain = false;
            $idttRecap = $('.idttRecap'),
            typedetransaction = '',
            $localisationRecap = $('.localisationRecap'),
            $localisationText = '',
            $budgetRecap = $('.budgetRecap'),
            pieces = '';

        patch5Plus();

        $('input[name="idtypebien"]:checked').each(function (i, input) {
            typedebien += typedebien ? ', ' : '';
            typedebien += $(input).next('label').find('span').text();

            $(input).closest(".child_block").prev('label').prev('input').attr("checked", true);

            if(input.value === '4') {//si typedebien est un terrain
                isTerrain = true;
            }

        });
        if 
(($("#block_type_bien_block_habitation_1").is(":checked") && 
$(".child_block.block_habitation:eq(0) input:checked").size() == 0) || 
($("#block_type_bien_block_habitation_2").is(":checked") && 
$(".child_block.block_habitation:eq(1) input:checked").size() == 0) || 
($("#block_type_bien_block_habitation_3").is(":checked") && 
$(".child_block.block_habitation:eq(2) input:checked").size() == 0)) {
            $('input[name="idtypebien"]:checked').attr("checked", false)
            typedebien = $(".mrHabitation input:checked").next('label').find('span').text();
        }
        if ($("#block_idtt_idtt_18").is(":checked")) {
            $("#block_type_bien_block_habitation_3").click();
            typedebien = "";
            $(".mrConstruction input:checked").each(function (i, input) {
                if (typedebien == "") {
                    typedebien += $(this).next('label').find('span').text();
                }
                else {
                    typedebien += ", " + $(this).next('label').find('span').text();
                }

            });

        }

        typedebien = typedebien || 'Type de bien';
        if (isTerrain === false && $(".piecesBlock input:not('.hiddenCriteria')").size() != 0) {
            $(".pieces").parent().removeClass("disabled");
            $('input[name="nb_pieces"]:checked').each(function (i, input) {
                pieces += pieces ? ', ' : '';
                pieces += $(input).val();
                pieces += $(input).val() == '5' ? '+' : '';

            });
            pieces = pieces ? '' + pieces : '1 et +';

        }
        else {
            pieces = "";
            $(".pieces").parent().addClass("disabled");
        }
        $(".piecesBlock .child_block").each(function () {

            if ($(this).find("input:not('.hiddenCriteria')").size() == 0) {
                $(this).find(".child_title").hide();
            }
            else {
                $(this).find(".child_title").hide().show();
            }

        })
        if ($(".mrSurface fieldset:not('.hiddenCriteria')").size() != 0) {
            $(".surface").parent().removeClass("disabled");
            var surface_min = $('input[name="surface_min"]').val();
            var surface_max = $('input[name="surface_max"]').val();
            var min, max, surface;
            if (surface_min == "" || surface_min == "undefined" || surface_min == "0") {
                min = 0;
            }
            if (surface_max == "" || surface_max == "undefined" || surface_max == "0") {
                max = 0;
            }

            if (min == 0 && max == 0) {
                $(".surface").addClass("empty");
                surface = "Surface min";
            }
            else if (min != 0 && max == 0) {
                surface = formatBudget(surface_min) + 'm² min';
                $(".surface").removeClass("empty");
            }
            else if (min == 0 && max != 0) {
                surface = formatBudget(surface_max) + 'm² max';
                $(".surface").removeClass("empty");
            }
            else if (min != 0 && max != 0) {
                surface = "De " + formatBudget(surface_min) + " à " + formatBudget(surface_max) + 'm²';
                $(".surface").removeClass("empty");
            }
        }
        else {
            surface = "";
            $(".surface").parent().addClass("disabled");
        }

        var budget_min = $('input[name="prix_min"]').val();
        var budget_max = $('input[name="prix_max"]').val();
        var bmin, bmax, budget;
        if (budget_min == "" || budget_min == "undefined" || budget_min == "0") {
            bmin = 0;
        }
        if (budget_max == "" || budget_max == "undefined" || budget_max == "0") {
            bmax = 0;
        }

        if (bmin == 0 && bmax == 0) {
            $(".budget").addClass("empty");
            budget = "Budget max";
        }
        else if (bmin != 0 && bmax == 0) {
            budget = 'à partir de ' + formatBudget(budget_min) + ' €';
            $(".budget").removeClass("empty");
        }
        else if (bmin == 0 && bmax != 0) {
            budget = formatBudget(budget_max) + ' € max';
            $(".budget").removeClass("empty");
        }
        else if (bmin != 0 && bmax != 0) {
            budget = "De " + formatBudget(budget_min) + " à " + formatBudget(budget_max) + ' €';
            $(".budget").removeClass("empty");
        }

        $('input[name="idtt"]:checked').each(function (i, input) {
            typedetransaction += typedetransaction ? ', ' : '';
            typedetransaction += $(input).next('label').find('span').text();
        });

        $('.refine__localisation_liste li').each(function (i, input) {
            $localisationText += $localisationText ? ', ' : '';
            $localisationText += $(this).data("label");
        });

        typedetransaction = typedetransaction || 'Type de transaction';

        $typedebienRecap.find('.typedebien').text(typedebien);
        $typedebienRecap.find('.pieces').text(pieces);
        $typedebienRecap.find('.surface').text(surface);

        $idttRecap.find('span').text(typedetransaction).attr('title', typedetransaction);
        $localisationRecap.find('span').text($localisationText);
        $budgetRecap.find('span').text(budget);

    };

    var programmesNeufsIsCheck = true;

    afterMetarefinerInit();

    //effectué après l'initialisation du refiner
    function afterMetarefinerInit() {
        var $programmesNeufs = $(".mrOption_achat");
        var search = document.location.search;

         if 
(search.match(/(idtt=[26])([^0-9]|$)/g) && 
!search.match(/(naturebien=1)([^,0-9]|$)/g)) { //achat + investir + (pas
 du vieux) 
            showCriterion($programmesNeufs);
            checkProgrammesNeufs(true);//neuf : pré check et affiché
        } else if(!search.match(/(idtt=[26])([^0-9]|$)/g)) {//tout sauf achat et investir (sans se préoccupé du vieux)
            checkProgrammesNeufs(true);//neuf : pré check et caché
        } else {
            checkProgrammesNeufs(false);//neuf : uncheck et caché
        }
        
    }

    function updateLimitsLabel() {
        var $block = $('.locationLimits'),
            $selected = $block.find('.selected').text(''),
            value = '';

        $block.find('input:checked').each(function (i, input) {
            value += i > 0 ? ', ' : '';
            value += $(input).next('label').text();
        });

        $selected.text(value);

    }

    function showCriterion(criterion) {
        criterion.removeClass('hiddenCriteria');
    }

    function hideCriterion(criterion) {
        criterion.addClass('hiddenCriteria');
    }

    function checkProgrammesNeufs(check) {
        var $programmesNeufsInput = $('#block_option_achat_naturebien_4');

        //on utilise .click pour appel de la fonction qui set le modelrefiner
        if (!$programmesNeufsInput.is(':checked') && check === true) {
            $programmesNeufsInput.click();//check
            programmesNeufsIsCheck = true;
        } else if($programmesNeufsInput.is(':checked') && check === false) {
            $programmesNeufsInput.click();//uncheck
            programmesNeufsIsCheck = false;
        }

        //dans le reste des cas on ne fait rien car on est dans le bon cas
    }

    function showProgrammesNeufs() {
        var $programmesNeufs = $(".mrOption_achat");

        if(programmesNeufsIsCheck) {
            showCriterion($programmesNeufs);
            checkProgrammesNeufs(true);
        } else {
            showCriterion($programmesNeufs);
            checkProgrammesNeufs(false);
        }
      
    }




    function optionSwitch() {
        var $programmesNeufs = $(".mrOption_achat");
        var $construction = $(".mrConstruction");
        var $location = $(".mrOption_location");
        var $typeCommerce = $(".mrOption_typecommerce");

        if ($("#block_idtt_idtt_1").is(":checked")) {//location
            
            if 
($("#block_type_bien_block_habitation_3").is(":checked") || 
$("#block_type_bien_block_habitation_2").is(":checked")) {
                //caché quand les blocs bureau/commerce/autres selectionnés
                hideCriterion($location);
            } else {
                //visible quand le bloc habitation est selectionné
                showCriterion($location);
            }

            hideCriterion($programmesNeufs);
            hideCriterion($typeCommerce);
            hideCriterion($construction);

        } else if ($("#block_idtt_idtt_2").is(":checked") ) {///cas achat 

            if($('.block_habitation 
#idtypebienchild\\.value6:checked, .block_habitation 
#idtypebienchild\\.value7:checked').size() > 0) {
                showCriterion($typeCommerce);
            } else {
                hideCriterion($typeCommerce);
            }

            if 
($("#block_type_bien_block_habitation_3").is(":checked") || 
$("#block_type_bien_block_habitation_2").is(":checked")) {
                 hideCriterion($programmesNeufs);
            }
            else {
                 showProgrammesNeufs();
            }

            hideCriterion($construction);
            hideCriterion($location);

        } else if ($("#block_idtt_idtt_6").is(":checked")) {///cas investir

            if 
($("#block_type_bien_block_habitation_3").is(":checked") || 
$("#block_type_bien_block_habitation_2").is(":checked")) {
                hideCriterion($programmesNeufs);
            }
            else {
                showProgrammesNeufs();
            }

             hideCriterion($construction);
             hideCriterion($location);
             hideCriterion($typeCommerce);

        } else if ($("#block_idtt_idtt_5").is(":checked")) {//VIAGER

            hideCriterion($construction);
            hideCriterion($location);
            hideCriterion($programmesNeufs);
            hideCriterion($typeCommerce);

        } else if ($("#block_idtt_idtt_18").is(":checked")) {//CONSTRUIRE

            showCriterion($construction);
            hideCriterion($location);
            hideCriterion($programmesNeufs);
            hideCriterion($typeCommerce);

        }
    }

    function updateLimits(query) {
        var $block = $('.locationLimits');

        $.get(location.protocol + '//www.seloger.com/ajax_refinerPreciserRecherche.json?' + query, function (res) {
            var limits = res.data;

            if (limits && limits.quartiers.length) {
                var $list = $block.find('.options'),
                    $defaultInput = $('<input type="checkbox" id="allLimits" checked="checked" />'),
                    $defaultLabel = $('<label for="allLimits">Tous les quartiers</label>'),
                    placesCodes = [],
                    $input, $label;

                $defaultLabel.data('place', limits.ville);

                $list.empty().append($defaultInput).append($defaultLabel);

                $('ul.refine__localisation_liste').find('li').each(function (i, li) {
                    placesCodes.push($(li).data('place').code);
                });

                $.each(limits.quartiers, function (i, quartier) {
                    $input = $('<input type="checkbox" id="quartier' + i + '" />');
                    $label = $('<label for="quartier' + i + '">' + quartier.value + '</label>');

                    $label.data('place', quartier);
                    $list.append($input).append($label);

                    if (placesCodes.indexOf(quartier.code) > -1) {
                        $defaultInput.prop('checked', false);
                        $input.prop('checked', true);
                    }
                });

                updateLimitsLabel();

                $block.css('display', 'inline-block');
            } else {
                $block.css('display', 'none');
            }
        });
    }

    function limitHandler() {
        var $input = $(this),
            $label = $input.next('label'),
            $allLimits = $('#allLimits'),
            $list = $("ul.refine__localisation_liste"),
            place = $label.data('place'),
            item;

        if ($input.is($allLimits)) {
            $input.nextAll('input').prop('checked', false);
            $input.prop('checked', true);
            item = $('<li data-action-criterion="change" class="selected_location">' + place.value + '<a class="refine__localisation_delete"> X </a>' + '</li>');
            
            $input.parent().find('label').each(function(i, item) {
                var itemChoice = jQuery.makeArray($list.children());
                var textChoice = itemChoice.map(function(item) {return $(item).clone().children().remove().end().text();});
                var listText = $(item).data('place').value;
                var index = textChoice.indexOf(listText);
                
                if(index !== -1) {
                    deleteItem = itemChoice[index];
                    $(deleteItem).remove();
                }
            });
            
        } else if ($input.is(':checked')) {
            $allLimits.prop('checked', false);
            $list.find('li').each(function () {
                if ($(this).data().place.code == $allLimits.next('label').data().place.code) {
                    $(this).remove();
                }
            });
            item = $('<li data-action-criterion="change" class="selected_location">' + place.value + '<a class="refine__localisation_delete"> X </a>' + '</li>');
        } else {
            $list.find('li').each(function () {
                if ($(this).data().place.code == place.code) {
                    $(this).remove();
                }
            });
        }

        if (item) {
            item.data('label', place.value);
            item.data('place', place);
            $list.append(item);
        }

        $('#search_localisation').blur();
        MetaRefiner.refinerUi.UpdateModel();

        updateLimitsLabel();


    }
    function dockControls() {
        var $elmt = $('.dockable'),
            fixedHeight = $(this).outerHeight(),
            sc = $(this).scrollTop(),
            elmtHeight = $elmt.outerHeight(),
            contentHeight = $('.mrMain').outerHeight(),
            contolsHeight = $('.controls').outerHeight();

        sc < contentHeight + contolsHeight - fixedHeight - elmtHeight ? $elmt.addClass('docked') : $elmt.removeClass('docked');
    }
    function openThisBlock() {
        if (!$(this).parent().hasClass("disabled")) {

            if ($(".mrLayout").size() == 0) {
                $('<div/>', {
                    id: 'mrLayout',
                    class: 'mrLayout hidden'
                }).appendTo('.metaRefinerHeader');

                $('#mrLayout').on('click', function () {
                    closeMrLayout() ;
                });
            }
            var $el = $('.' + $(this).attr('id') + 'Block');
            if ($el.hasClass("open")) {
                $el.removeClass('open').hide();
                $(".mrLayout").hide();
                $(".metaRefinerHeader .onfocus").removeClass('onfocus');
                $(".openMetaRefiner.active").removeClass('active');
                MetaRefiner.refinerUi.UpdateModel();
                if(pageList)
                {refreshList(MetaRefiner, true, pageList, pageMap);}
                if(pageMap)
                {refreshMap(true);}
                if(pageVenteAcheter)
                {cb()}

            }
            else {
                $(".metaRefinerHeader .refineItem .open").removeClass('open').hide();
                $(".metaRefinerHeader .onfocus").removeClass('onfocus');
                $el.addClass('open').show();
                $(".mrLayout").show();
                $(this).parent().addClass('onfocus');
                if ($(this).hasClass("openMetaRefiner")) {
                    $(this).addClass('active');
                } else {
                    $(".openMetaRefiner").removeClass('active');
                }
                if ($(this).hasClass("budget")) {
                    $("input[name='prix_max']").focus();
                }
                else if ($(this).hasClass("surface")) {
                    $("input[name='surface_min']").focus();
                }
                if(pageVenteAcheter)
                {cb()}
            }
        }
    }

    var onSearch = function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        var $errorMsg = $('.errorMsg');
        var button = $(this);

        if ($errorMsg.length) {
            var pos = $errorMsg.first().closest('fieldset').position().top;
            $('.mainContent').animate({scrollTop: pos}, 500);
        } else {
            if ($('.mainContent').is('.open')) {
                $('.openMetaRefiner').click();
            }
            if ($('.typedebienContent').is('.open')) {
                $('.typedebienRecap').click();
            }
            $(".openMetaRefiner.active").removeClass('active');
            //Disable submit buttons to avoid spam click
            button.prop('disabled', true);

            if(pageList)
            { refreshList(MetaRefiner, true, pageList, pageMap).then(function () {
                //Restore button state when list has been displayed
                button.prop('disabled', false);
            });}
            if(pageMap)
            { refreshMap(true);
            }

            if(pageVenteAcheter)
            {
                refreshListPageVenteAcheter(MetaRefiner)
            }
        }

        if (!pageMap && typeof(_setClickArticleListing) != "undefined") {
            _setClickArticleListing();
        }
    };

    $('.mrSearchButton, .glassButton').click(onSearch);

    $('.switch_to_map, .go-to-map .gtm-circle').click(function (e) {
        if (!$(this).hasClass('on')) {
            e.preventDefault();
            var mapQuery = MetaRefiner.refiner.GetQuery();

            if (mapQuery.indexOf('idpays') === -1) {
                mapQuery = mapQuery.replace('&fraicheur=14', '')
                    .replace('&rayon=', '&rayondesactive=')
                    .replace('&bd=CartoToList_SL', '');

                location.href = location.protocol + '//www.seloger.com/map.htm?' + mapQuery + "&bd=ListToCarto_SL";
            }
        }
    });
    $('.switch_to_list').click(function (e) {
        if (!$(this).hasClass('on')) {
            e.preventDefault();
            var mapQuery = MetaRefiner.refiner.GetQuery();

            if (mapQuery.indexOf('idpays') === -1) {
                mapQuery = mapQuery.replace('&fraicheur=14', '')

                    .replace('&bd=ListToCarto_SL', '');

                location.href = location.protocol + '//www.seloger.com/list.htm?' + mapQuery + "&bd=CartoToList_SL";
            }
        }
    });

    function refreshMap(pushState) {
        var loader = $('.liste_resultat > .loader');
        //Event for Avatag
        var e = document.createEvent('CustomEvent');
        e.initEvent('searchRefine', true, true);
        document.body.dispatchEvent(e);
        var query = MetaRefiner.refiner.GetQuery();

        $(".metaRefinerHeader .open").removeClass("open");
        $(".metaRefinerHeader .onfocus").removeClass("onfocus");
        $("#mrLayout").hide();
        $(".mrHabitation").removeClass("hiddenCriteria");
        $(".mrConstruction").addClass("hiddenCriteria");

        if ($("#block_idtt_idtt_18").is(":checked")) {
            $(".mrHabitation").addClass("hiddenCriteria");
            $(".mrConstruction").removeClass("hiddenCriteria");
        }

        var query = MetaRefiner.patchQuery(query);


        if (window.history && window.history.pushState) {
            if(pushState) {

                var newUrl = 'http://www.seloger.com/map.htm?' + query;
                history.pushState({refineModel : MetaRefiner.refineModel}, null, newUrl);
            }
        } else {
            document.location.href = 'http://www.seloger.com/map.htm?' + query;
            return true;
        }

        // Display loader
        loader.show();*/

        var AnnonceFactory = function () {
        };
        AnnonceFactory.prototype = {
            CreateElement: function (response, annonce, index, page) {
                // on ajoute une classe pour différencier les annonces localisées et non localisées
                var hyphen = response.data.hyphen;
                var mustache_pub_content="";
                var evarPage=page+1;

                if(response.data.data.pub.vignette_cp && index==4)
                {
                    mustache_pub_content = Mustache.to_html($("#template-pubCp-map").html(), response.data.data.pub);
                }
                // vignette dep après la 7è annonce
                else if (response.data.data.pub.vignette_dp && index == 7) {
                    mustache_pub_content = Mustache.to_html($("#template-pubDp-map").html(), response.data.data.pub);
                }
                var mustache_article_content = Mustache.to_html($("#template-listing-map").html(), annonce);
                return {
                    htmlContent: mustache_pub_content + mustache_article_content,
                    data: annonce,
                    id: annonce.id
                };
            }
        };
        var AnnonceVedette = function () {
        };
        AnnonceVedette.prototype = {
            GetElements: function (request) {
                //a custom
                var url = 'http://www.seloger.com/list,json,vedette_list.json';

                return 
SeLoger.Utils.HttpUtils.Get(url, request.search + '&LISTING-LISTpg='
 + request.page).then(function (response) {
                    if (response.listingList && response.title && response.title.numListings) {
                        return {
                            list: response.listingList,
                            total: parseInt(response.title.numListings)
                        };
                    }
                    else {
                        return null;
                    }
                });

            }
        };

        var AnnonceService = function() {
        };
        AnnonceService.prototype = {
            GetElements: function (request) {
                 query = request.search.replace("naturebien=4", "naturebien=1,2,4");
                var url = 'http://www.seloger.com/map,geo-liste-annonces';
                return 
SeLoger.Utils.HttpUtils.Get(url, query + '&LISTING-LISTpg=' + 
request.page).then(function (response) {


                    if (response.data.annonces && response.data.numResults > 0) {

                        return {
                            data: response,
                            list: response.data.annonces,
                            total: response.data.numResults,
                            nbPages: response.data.nbPages
                        };
                    }
                    else if(response.data.numResults == 0)
                    {
                        return {
                            data: response,
                            list: [],
                            total: 0,
                            nbPages: 0
                        };

                    }
                    else {
                        return null;
                    }
                });
            }
        };
        function mustach_vedette(query) {

            var url = 'http://www.seloger.com/list,json,offresphares.json?' + query;
            var listingListTemplate = $("#template-vedette-map").html();
            var listingList = $(".flagship ul");
            $.get(url, function(data){
                //$(".liste_resultat").addClass("fullheight");

                if ( (data.phare=="" || !data.phare ) && (data.phare_cmi_sl=="" || !data.phare_cmi_sl ) )
                {
                    if (!$(".liste_resultat").hasClass("fullheight")) {
                        $(".flagship").slideUp("slow", function () {
                            $(".liste_resultat").addClass("fullheight");
                            superList.withVedette = false;
                        })
                    }
                }
                else {
                    superList.withVedette = true;
                    $(".liste_resultat").removeClass("fullheight")
                    $(".flagship").slideDown("slow");
                }

                if (typeof(sliderVedette)!="undefined")
                {sliderVedette.destroySlider();}
                if (listingListTemplate) {
                    listingList.html(Mustache.to_html(listingListTemplate, data))
                }
                if($(".flagship ul li").size()>1)
                {
                    sliderVedette = $('.right_column .flagship ul').bxSlider({
                        maxSlides: 2,
                        moveSlides: 1,
                        slideWidth: 200,
                        slideMargin: 5,
                        infiniteLoop: false,
                        hideControlOnEnd: true,
                        touchEnabled: true,
                        swipeThreshold: 50,
                        oneToOneTouch: false,
                        preventDefaultSwipeX: true,
                        preventDefaultSwipeY: false,
                        pager: false,
                        auto: false,
                        caption: true
                    });
                    $(".bx-prev").addClass("disabled");
                }
            })
        }

        function initCarousel(selector) {

            var size = $(selector).find(".container_image_map").width();

            $(selector).find(".container_image_map .carousel:not(.with-slides-js)").each(function (index, item) {
                var imgs = $(item).find('img');

                if (imgs.length > 1) {
                    $(item).slidesjs({
                        width: size,
                        height: size,
                        navigation: true
                    });
                    $(item).addClass('with-slides-js');
                }
            });
        }
        var MultiList = function(selectorList, factory, service) {
            var that = this;

            this.nbCountList = undefined;
            this.titleCount = " ";
            this.firstLoad = true;
            this.hideVedettePixel = 1000;

            this.pixelScroll = 0;
            this.withVedette = false;
            this.list = new SeLoger.List.InfinityList(
                $(selectorList)[0],
                {
                    onLoadStart: function() {},
                    onLoadEnd: function(){
                        that.onListLoad.apply(that, arguments);
                    },
                    onClickElement: function(e) {},
                    onScroll: function(pixel) {
                        that.pixelScroll = pixel;
                        that.onScroll();
                    },
                    onOverElement: function (e) {
                        map.CloseAllAnnonce();
                        map.OpenAnnonce(parseInt(e.data.id));
                    },
                    onOutElement: function (e) {
                        map.CloseAllAnnonce();
                        map.CloseAnnonce(parseInt(e.data.id));
                    },
                    activateRequest: 1000 //pixel avant la fin
                },
                new factory(),
                new service(1)
            );
        };
        MultiList.prototype = {
            onScroll: function () {
                var jQ_vedette = $('.right_column .flagship');
                var jQ_liste = $('.right_column .liste_resultat');

                if((this.pixelScroll > this.hideVedettePixel) && this.withVedette) {
                    jQ_vedette.hide();
                    jQ_liste.addClass('fullheight');
                } else if(this.pixelScroll <= this.hideVedettePixel) {
                    jQ_vedette.show();
                    jQ_liste.removeClass('fullheight');
                }
            },

            loadAllList: function(query) {
                this.nbCountList = this.hyphen = undefined;
                this.firstLoad = true;
                this.separator = false;

                return this.list.reload({ search: query, page: 1}).then(function() {
                    mustach_vedette(query);
                });
            },

            onAddAnnonceFavorisSuccess: function(idAnnonce) {
                for(var i = 0 ; i < this.list.elements.length ; i ++) {
                    if(this.list.elements[i].id.toString() === idAnnonce.toString()) {
                        var el = 
$(".liste_resultat #annonce-" + this.list.elements[i].data.id + "-" + 
this.list.elements[i].data.publicationId + " .add_fav_map");
                        
el.removeClass("action-add").addClass("action-succes").find("button").attr("data-tooltip",
 "Supprimer des favoris");
                    }
                }
            },

            onDeleteAnnonceFavorisSuccess: function(idAnnonce) {
                for(var i = 0 ; i < this.list.elements.length ; i ++) {
                    if(this.list.elements[i].id.toString() === idAnnonce.toString()) {
                        var el = 
$(".liste_resultat #annonce-" + this.list.elements[i].data.id + "-" + 
this.list.elements[i].data.publicationId + " .add_fav_map");
                        
el.removeClass("action-succes").addClass("action-add").find("button").attr("data-tooltip",
 "Ajouter aux favoris");
                    }
                }
            },

            initAnnoncesFavoris: function() {
                var that = this;
                if(window.EspacePerso && window.EspacePerso.DevApi) {
                    window.EspacePerso.DevApi.recupererAnnoncesIds(function(annonces) {
                        annonces.forEach(function(annonceId) {
                            that.onAddAnnonceFavorisSuccess(annonceId);
                        });
                    });
                }
            },

            onListLoad: function(data, elements, total) {

                initCarousel('.right_column 
.liste_resultat .annonce_map.Or, .right_column .liste_resultat 
.annonce_map.PolePo');
                this.nbCountList = parseInt(total);
                this.titleCount = data.data.title;
                if (this.firstLoad === true) {
                    this.onAllListLoadFirstTime(data.data.hyphen);
                }
                this.addClassToPropertyRows(this.hyphen, total);

                this.initAnnoncesFavoris();
            },

            onAllListLoadFirstTime: function(hyphen) {
                var that = this;

                this.firstLoad = false;
                this.hyphen = hyphen;
                $(".type_annonces").text("");

                if (this.nbCountList != 0) {
                    var txt1 = "annonce ";
                    var txt1b = "localisée ";
                    var txt1c = "dans la zone";
                    var txt2 = "annonce ";
                    var txt2b = "non localisée ";

                    var nbtotal = parseInt(this.nbCountList);
                    var localizedCount = hyphen - 1;
                    var unlocalizedCount = nbtotal - localizedCount;
                    var texttitle = nbtotal > 1 ? "annonces " : "annonce ";

                    $(".title_nbresult").text(SELOGER.UTILS.formatMillier(nbtotal));
                    $(".title_wrapper h1").text(texttitle);

                    if(hyphen !== undefined && localizedCount > 0) {
                        $(".type_annonces").html('dont ' + SELOGER.UTILS.formatMillier(localizedCount) + ' sur la carte');
                    }
                }
                else {
                    var $popup = $('#drawingPopup');
                    if(this.nbCountList == 0) {

                        /*var flag = refiner.GetModel().places.length;

                         if (flag) {
                         
$popup.find('span').text("Aucun résultat. Supprimez les critères 
discriminants ou élargissez la zone de recherche");
                         } else {
                         
$popup.find('span').text("Aucun résultat. Votre dernière recherche a été
 effacée, renseignez une localité pour obtenir des résultats");
                         }*/

                        $popup.fadeIn();
                    }
                    else {
                        $popup.fadeOut();
                    }
                    // On n'a pas de résultats dans la liste 2, donc on n'affiche que la première liste, et on
                    // n'affiche pas les onglets
                    var texteA = "annonces";
                    $(".head_list").hide();
                    $(".title_nbresult").text(this.nbCountList);
                    if (this.nbCountList<=1)
                    {texteA="annonce"}
                    $(".title_wrapper h1").text(texteA);
                    $(".type_annonces").html(this.titleCount);
                }
                if($(".refine__limit").css("display")=="none")
                {$('.refine__broaden').hide();}
                else{$('.refine__broaden').show();}


                var event = window.EspacePerso && window.EspacePerso.Events ? window.EspacePerso.Events : null;

                if(event) {
                    event.on('EVENT_CONNECT_SUCCESS', function() {
                        that.initAnnoncesFavoris();
                    });
                    event.on('EVENT_ANNOUNCE_ADD_SUCCESS', function(params) {
                        that.onAddAnnonceFavorisSuccess(params.IdAnnonce);
                        onAddAnnonceFavorisSuccessMap(params.IdAnnonce);
                    });

                    event.on('EVENT_ANNOUNCE_DELETE_SUCCESS', function (params) {
                        that.onDeleteAnnonceFavorisSuccess(params.IdAnnonce);
                        onDeleteAnnonceFavorisSuccessMap(params.IdAnnonce);
                    });
                }
            },

            addClassToPropertyRows: function (hyphen, nbTotal) {
                // adding classes
                var count = 1;
                var rowClass = 'localized';
                var unlocalizedCount = parseInt(nbTotal - (parseInt(hyphen) - 1));
                var that = this;
                $('.liste_resultat > ul > li').each(function(){
                    if (!$(this).hasClass('localized') && !$(this).hasClass('unlocalized')) {
                        if (count >= hyphen) {
                            rowClass = 'unlocalized';
                        }
                        $(this).addClass(rowClass);

                        if (rowClass === 'unlocalized' && that.separator === false) {
                            // ajout du séparateur texte entre les annonces localisées et non localisées
                            $separator = $('<li class="separateur">' + unlocalizedCount + (unlocalizedCount > 1 ? ' annonces ' : ' annonce ') + 'sans adresse renseignée<button class="delete_title_idq"></button></li>');
                            $separator.children('.delete_title_idq').on('click', function() {
                                $(this).parent('.separateur').hide();
                            });
                            $('li.localized + .unlocalized').before($separator);
                            that.separator = true;
                        }
                    }
                    count++;
                });
            }
        };

        return document.querySelector('#lifemap-app').aurelia.root.viewModel.router.navigate('map.htm?'+ query);


        // loader.show();

        // });
    }

    //handles search page button
    function refreshListPageVenteAcheter(MetaRefiner, pushState) {
        var query = MetaRefiner.refiner.GetQuery();

        query = MetaRefiner.patchQuery(query);

        document.location.href = location.protocol + '//www.seloger.com/list.htm?' + query;
        return true;
    }

    }

    }



    function closeMrLayout() {
        $(".metaRefinerHeader .open").removeClass("open");
        $(".openMetaRefiner.active").removeClass("active");
        $(".mrLayout").hide();
        $(".metaRefinerHeader .onfocus").removeClass("onfocus");
        // si bouton «- de critères»
        $('.openMetaRefiner.active').removeClass('active');

        MetaRefiner.refinerUi.UpdateModel();
        if(pageList) {
            refreshList(MetaRefiner, true, pageList, pageMap);
        }
        if(pageMap) {
            refreshMap(true);
        }
        if(pageVenteAcheter)
        {cb()}
    }

    $('.mrClose, .mrLayout').on('click', function () {
        closeMrLayout() ;
    });

    if(typeof(map)!="undefined") {
        var refiner = MetaRefiner.refiner;
        var refinerUi = MetaRefiner.refinerUi;
        function getPolygons() {
            var model = refiner.GetModel(),
                polygons = [];

            $.each(model.places, function (i, place) {
                place.param == 'polygon' ? polygons.push(place) : '';
            });

            return polygons;
        }
        function lassoHandler(map) {
            var polygons = getPolygons(),
                $lasso = $('#lasso'),
                $popup = $('#drawingPopup'),
                message = '';

            if (polygons.length >= 3) {
                message = 'Vous pouvez dessiner au maximum 3 zones de recherche';
            } else if ($lasso.hasClass('off')) {
                message = 'Zoomez pour dessiner la zone de recherche de votre choix';
            } else {
                if (!polygons.length) {
                    map.ClearSearch();
                }
                message = 'Dessinez sur la carte la zone de votre choix';
                map.StartDrawing();
            }

            $popup.find('span').text(message);
            $popup.fadeIn();
        }
        var onSearchDone = function () {
            var $lassoCancel = $('#lasso-cancel'),
                polygons = getPolygons();

            polygons.length ? $lassoCancel.show() : $lassoCancel.hide();
        };

        var onShapeStatus = function (flag) {
            //$('#drawingPopup').fadeOut();
            var polygons = getPolygons(),
                $lasso = $('#lasso');

            flag = flag && polygons.length < 3;
            flag ? $lasso.removeClass('off') : $lasso.addClass('off');
        };

        onSearchDone();
        onShapeStatus();
        var mapConfig = map.mapFactory.config;
        mapConfig.onSearchDone = onSearchDone;
        mapConfig.onShapeStatus = onShapeStatus;}

}

</script>

<script>
    $(function () {

        function underscoreToCamelCase(str) {

            var arr = str.split("_");

            for(var i = 0, n = arr.length; i < n; i++) {
                arr[i] = arr[i].charAt(0).toUpperCase() + arr[i].slice(1);
            }

            return arr.join("");
        }

        var ns = underscoreToCamelCase("listing");
        var moduleName = underscoreToCamelCase("list");
        if( SL[ns] && SL[ns][moduleName])
        {
            if (typeof(SL[ns][moduleName].init)!="undefined")
                SL[ns][moduleName].init();
        }

    });
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">


    var cFootDom = document,
        cFoot = document.querySelector('#c-foot');
    if (cFoot) cFootDom = cFoot.shadowRoot;

    function fFooterToggle(element){
        var footer = cFootDom.querySelectorAll(".c-foot-kick .c-wrap > div"),
            footerPart1 = footer[0],
            footerPart2 = footer[1];

        if (element.innerHTML == "+"){
            footerPart1.classList.remove('u-hide-sm');
            footerPart2.classList.remove('u-hide-sm');
            element.innerHTML = "-";
        } else{
            footerPart1.classList.add('u-hide-sm');
            footerPart2.classList.add('u-hide-sm');
            element.innerHTML = "+";
        }
    }

							<div id="newsletter">
    <p class="u-padl-300">NEWSLETTER, les guides et astuces SeLoger</p>

    <form class="f-newsletter" action="" method="post" novalidate>
        <input type="email" id="newsletter-email" name="newsletter-email" autocomplete="off">
        <label id="lbl-newsletter-email" for="newsletter-email">Email</label>
        <button class="b-btn b-warn" type="submit" id="newsletter-submit">M'abonner</button>

        <div id="newsletter-message" class="alert alert-danger" style="display: none"></div>
    </form>
</div>
							
							<script type="text/javascript">
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',function () {
    var $form   = $('#newsletter').find('form'),
    $email  = $form.find('#newsletter-email'),
    $submit = $form.find('#newsletter-submit'),
    $label = $form.find('#lbl-newsletter-email'),
    $error  = $form.find('#newsletter-message');


    if ($email.val()) {
      $label.addClass('focused');
    }

    /**
     * Validate given email string.
     *
     * @param email {string}
     * @returns {boolean}
     */
    function validateEmail(email) {
      var regex = /^([\w-]+(?:\.[\w-]+)*)@((?:[\w-]+\.)*\w[\w-]{0,66})\.([a-z]{2,6}(?:\.[a-z]{2})?)$/i;

      return regex.test(email);
    }

    $email.on('keyup', function () {
      var email = $(this).val();

      if (validateEmail(email)) {
        $submit.addClass('is-active');
      } else {
        $submit.removeClass('is-active');
      }
    });

    $email.on('focusout keydown', function () {
      $error.hide();
    });

    $(document).on('click', function () {
      $error.hide();
    });

    $email.on('focusout', function () {
      if ($(this).val()) {
        $label.addClass('focused');
      } else {
        $label.removeClass('focused');
      }
    });

    $form.on('submit', function (e) {
      e.preventDefault();

      if (validateEmail($email.val())) {
            // Subscription to the newsletter
            $.ajax({
              type:    "GET",
              url:     "ajax-newsletter.json",
              data:    { 'email': $email.val() },
              success: function (response) {
                if (response) {
                  var codeResult = response.code;

                  if(codeResult == null || codeResult == undefined){
                    $form.addClass('shake');
                    $error.show();
                    $error.text('Oups ! L’abonnement a raté... Vérifiez votre email et essayez à nouveau.');

                    setTimeout(function () {
                      $form.removeClass('shake');
                    }, 600);
                  }

                  else if ($.inArray(codeResult, [0, 1, 2, 3]) !== -1) {
                    $submit.addClass('is-done is-active b-fresh');
                    $submit.text('Merci !');
                    //prevents multiple clicks on newsletter
                    $('#newsletter-email').prop( "disabled", true );
                  }

                  else if ($.inArray(codeResult, [4, 5, 6, 8]) !== -1) {
                    $form.addClass('shake');
                    $error.show();
                    $error.text('Oups ! L’abonnement a raté... Vérifiez votre email et essayez à nouveau.');

                    setTimeout(function () {
                      $form.removeClass('shake');
                    }, 600);
                  }
                  else if (codeResult === 7) {
                    $form.addClass('shake');
                    $error.show();
                    $error.text('Oups ! L’abonnement a raté... Votre email est trop long pour nous.');

                    setTimeout(function () {
                      $form.removeClass('shake');
                    }, 600);
                  }
                  else if ($.inArray(codeResult, [9, 10]) !== -1) {
                    $form.addClass('shake');
                    $error.show();
                    $error.text('Oups ! L’abonnement a raté... Essayez avec un autre email peut-être ?');

                    setTimeout(function () {
                      $form.removeClass('shake');
                    }, 600);
                  }
                  else {
                    $form.addClass('shake');
                    $error.show();
                    $error.text('Oups ! L’abonnement a raté... Vérifiez votre email et essayez à nouveau.');

                    setTimeout(function () {
                      $form.removeClass('shake');
                    }, 600);
                  }
                }
                else {
                  $form.addClass('shake');
                  $error.show();
                  $error.text('Oups ! L’abonnement a raté... Vérifiez votre email et essayez à nouveau.');

                  setTimeout(function () {
                    $form.removeClass('shake');
                  }, 600);
                }
              }
            });
      } else {

        var textError = "";
        if($email.val().length===0){
          textError = "Renseigner un email";
        } else{
          textError = "Renseigner un email valide";
        }

        $form.addClass('shake');
        $error.show();

        $error.text(textError);

        setTimeout(function () {
          $form.removeClass('shake');
        }, 600);
      }
    });
  },false);
</script>
